# Portfolio-RMichels Overview

- Personal portfolio at [rmichels.com](https://rmichels.com): PHP + MySQL + Apache (LAMP), **no framework** (intentional).
- One PHP file per route at repo root; `.htaccess` strips `.php` from URLs.
- Templates: `Partial::build('partialName', $args)` loads `src/partials/{name}.php`.
- Project metadata from MySQL; case study body content is hardcoded in each `{slug}.php`.
- `skills/` = PHP showcase pages, **not** Cursor agent skills.
- Do not refactor application logic unless explicitly asked.

## Page bootstrap

```php
require "config.php";
require "src/Partial.php";
require "src/objects/Project.php";
Partial::build('header', ["about" => TRUE]);
// content
Partial::build('footer');
```

Subdirectory pages (`skills/`, `development/`): use `__DIR__ . "/../"` requires; `development/` pages need `chdir('../')` first.

## Slug coupling

PHP filename = DB `project_slug` = `assets/img/{slug}.jpg` (hero image). Keep all three aligned.
